  "logNo": "110159934901",
  "title": "[남성역사당역체형교정이수한의원]척추측만증/일자목",
  "addDate": "2013. 2. 16.",
  "categoryNo": "14",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110159934901",
  "html_size": 189773,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110159934901\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110159934901\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">척추측</span></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #3a32c3\">만증</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"></span></strong><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">현대사회에서 컴퓨터는 기본으로 사용합니다. </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">하지만 잘못된 자세로 인해 척추가 휘어 측만증으로 이어집니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">척추측만증이란, 척추가 정면에서 보았을떄 옆으로 굽은것을 말합니다.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d6d1dbf7feb1dfa.png\" width=\"383\" height=\"376\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 383px; rheight: 376px\" id=\"20130216_4/isuhani_1361002172008tdLx2_PNG/%C3%B4%C3%DF%C3%F8%B8%B81.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A60B35B5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d6d1dbf7feb1dfa.png\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">바른자세를 습관화 하지 않는다면 어깨와허리 통증으로 생활하는데에 불편함을 호소 할 것입니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">우리의 척추는 뒤에서 보았을때 일직선으로 곧아야 하고 옆에서 보았을 때는 허리는 앞으로 볼록</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">등은 뒤로 볼록, 목은 다시 앞으로 볼록한 커브가 잘 유지되어야 합니다&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e76b9027b68cb96.png\" width=\"174\" height=\"290\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 174px; rheight: 290px\" id=\"20130216_216/isuhani_1361004225659k6Q1V_PNG/%C3%F8%B8%B8%C1%F52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A60B35B5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6e76b9027b68cb96.png\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">척추 측만증의 증상</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">척추측만증은 키가 성장하는 시기에 급격하게 나타날수가 있어서 조기 발견이 중요합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">몸이 한쪽으로 기울어져 있거나 허리의 중심선이 휘어져 있거나 어깨의 높이가 차이가 날 경우</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">골반이 평행하지 않고 기울어져 있을 경우 의심을 할수있다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ec4e36cb6dcfe847.png\" width=\"543\" height=\"344\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 543px; rheight: 344px\" id=\"20130216_294/isuhani_1361004034221WIAz0_PNG/%C3%F8%B8%B8%C1%F5%C7%A5.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A60B35B5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ec4e36cb6dcfe847.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">일자목은 대부분 측만증과 동반하는 경우가 많습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">정상적인 목은 C자형인데 책상에 나쁜자세로 장시간 오래 앉아 있거나 컴퓨터를 하게 되면 일자목(거북목)</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">턱이 앞으로 나오는 현상을 말합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_210/isuhani_1358995078999FYEhd_JPEG/%C1%A4%BB%F3_%B0%E6%C3%DF_%BF%A2%BD%BA%B7%B9%C0%CC.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"245\" height=\"206\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 245px; rheight: 206px\" id=\"20130124_210/isuhani_1358995078999FYEhd_JPEG/%C1%A4%BB%F3_%B0%E6%C3%DF_%BF%A2%BD%BA%B7%B9%C0%CC.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A60B35B5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_210/isuhani_1358995078999FYEhd_JPEG/%C1%A4%BB%F3_%B0%E6%C3%DF_%BF%A2%BD%BA%B7%B9%C0%CC.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_21/isuhani_1358995079281wGwny_JPEG/%C0%CF%C0%DA%B8%F1_%BF%A2%BD%BA%B7%B9%C0%CC.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"259\" height=\"194\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 259px; rheight: 194px\" id=\"20130124_21/isuhani_1358995079281wGwny_JPEG/%C0%CF%C0%DA%B8%F1_%BF%A2%BD%BA%B7%B9%C0%CC.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A60B35B5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_21/isuhani_1358995079281wGwny_JPEG/%C0%CF%C0%DA%B8%F1_%BF%A2%BD%BA%B7%B9%C0%CC.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 정상c자형&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 일자목</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #ef007c\"><u></u></span></u>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #ef007c\"><u></u></span></u>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #ef007c\"><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt\"><strong>[아래글은 이수한의원에서 30대 남성분이 치료 받으셨던 분의 내용입니다]</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 정형외과에서 X레이 촬영을 했었는데 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">병명은 <strong><span style=\"COLOR: #ff0000\">일자목과 척추측만증 </span></strong>이라고 하셨습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;어깨통증은 2012년 가을경에 발병해서 정형외과에서 물리치료를 시작했지만 아무런 효과가 없어서 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 이수한의원에 내원하게 되었고 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">원장님과 상담 후 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">체형교정프로그램에 등록을 하게되어 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 추나요법, 교정침치료, 부항치료를 받고</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">효과를 보시고 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">만족해 하셨습니다</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 치료받기전 평소에는 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">어깨와 목의 통증으로 생활하기 불편 하였으나 치료후 생활하는데에는 </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 불편함이 없어지고 좋아 지셨습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 항상 궁금한 질문에 친절하게 대답해 주시는 원장님과 선생님들께 감사합니다&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;라고 말씀을 </span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: 굴림,gulim\">주셨습니다.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_117/isuhani_1358997723868F3nqK_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 193px; rheight: 48px\" id=\"20130124_117/isuhani_1358997723868F3nqK_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A60B35B5')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130124_117/isuhani_1358997723868F3nqK_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://blog.naver.com/isuhani\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.naver.com/isuhani</a><span style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: none\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
